JOHANNESBURG - A memorial service for Ontlametse Phalatse will be held in Hebron in the North West on Wednesday. The 18-year-old motivational speaker died a week ago at the George Mukhari Hospital, north of Pretoria.READ: Ontlametse Phalatse has diedShe had experienced breathing problems shortly before her death.Onlametsi was born with an extremely rare genetic disorder known as progeria, which causes a child s body to age rapidly.eNCA